metadata.name: It's On — Pleasure #1
metadata.description:
Edition 1 of 1
4928 × 3696 px

This is a collection of fine art images created in collaboration with Office magazine, NY. 

"pretty much every kind of bizarre — but amazing — sex toy you could ever think of: wanna whack off while you work out? There’s the Magic Ball. Like to get high and get off at the same time? Buy a glass penis bong. Got a thing for feet? Enter the vajankle… Literally."

[published in Office magazine, issue 12](http://officemagazine.net/its-on).
